1:
A declaration about Moab.\q1 Indeed, in one night Ar of Moab is laid waste and destroyed;
\q1 indeed, in one night Kir of Moab is laid waste and destroyed.
\q1

5:
My heart cries out for Moab; her fugitives flee to Zoar and to Eglath Shelishiyah.\q1 They go up the ascent of Luhith weeping;
\q1 on the road to Horonaim they loudly wail over their destruction.
\q1
